âœ… Rich Text Editing (Bold, Italics, Font Size, etc.)
âœ… Form Submission (Hidden Inputs to Capture Data)
âœ… Offline PDF & Excel Generation using JavaScript
âœ… No Database or Server-Side Storage Required


